},{"name":"places/ChIJX-T-t9KeToYRUb1poSSib8k/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLMkx2TWVnEAE","relativePublishTimeDescription":"4 years ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Great services! I had a leak in my AC unit and when I called, a technician was here shortly after. He was considerate, enlightening, & even called to say he was running a little behind. He gave me great guidelines on how to maintain my AC unit as well. I would highly recommend Sheffield Heating & Air Conditioning!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Great services! I had a leak in my AC unit and when I called, a technician was here shortly after. He was considerate, enlightening, & even called to say he was running a little behind. He gave me great guidelines on how to maintain my AC unit as well. I would highly recommend Sheffield Heating & Air Conditioning!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Paul Nixon","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114341050209332919947/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7YQH_TfjuCPgwS8Do6ZWBc_NrXWketaxs5gzbKNEXo50p17Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2021-04-29T09:33:55.328176Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLMkx2TWVnEAE&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURLMkx2TWVnEAE!2m1!1s0x864e9ed2b7fee45f:0xc96fa224a169bd51"},{"name":"places/ChIJX-T-t9KeToYRUb1poSSib8k/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURVazVqa3lBRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"6 years ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"This company is  reliable, professional and efficient. We have called them for problems that needed an urgent solution and they have always been very helpful. Ian has helped us out with a number of issues with heating & air and working with him has been great.  We really appreciate friendly and helpful people at Sheffield Heating & Air Conditioning and highly recommend them.","languag